# {{projectName}}

This is an API Platform project created with the MultiTech CLI.

## Requirements

- PHP 8.1 or higher
- Composer
- Symfony CLI (optional, but recommended)
- MySQL 5.7+ or PostgreSQL 9.6+ (if you use the default database)

## Installation

1. Clone this repository
2. Run `composer install`
3. Copy `.env` to `.env.local` and adjust the values
4. Run `php bin/console doctrine:database:create`
5. Run `php bin/console doctrine:schema:create`

## Usage

### Development

```bash
# Start the Symfony development server
symfony server:start

# Or use PHP's built-in server
php -S localhost:8000 -t public/
```

### API Documentation

The API documentation is available at:
- [API Platform UI](http://localhost:8000/api)
- [Swagger UI](http://localhost:8000/api/docs.json)

### Testing

```bash
# Run PHPUnit tests
php bin/phpunit
```

## Features

- [API Platform](https://api-platform.com/) for building API-first applications
- [Symfony](https://symfony.com/) as the underlying framework
- [Doctrine ORM](https://www.doctrine-project.org/projects/orm.html) for database access
- [JWT Authentication](https://jwt.io/) for secure API access

